Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面就是桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这桥的气氛不错嘛  我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好走过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  还撑得住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流了一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是住在这附近的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座桥已经支撑不住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去的时候也还要过去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要在这里停留多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识寄这封信的人么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路途遥远辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的女儿花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约三年前  她从那个藤桥上掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但之后就一直那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会向着太阳的方向发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也找了很多医生看过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有发现头上有被撞过的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然不知道为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  花怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你们原来很要好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把花变成那个样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了！请你一定要救她！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能带我去那个谷底一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  告诉我花掉下山谷时候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我说  别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我已经躲不开了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本家来提亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果拒绝的话  给这个村子的资助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会停止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能拒绝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人全部都会被村里处以私刑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母是理解我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母如果真心希望你得到幸福的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定能够忍耐的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果留下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无法按照自己的愿望生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们离开这个山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻过山去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到宽广明亮的土地上去生活吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起走吧！花！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点！那里有一点脆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样只有我们逃走  是不会幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会忍受的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善你会一直想着我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会一直思念着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算到了那边  心会压抑而死  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先过桥去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来掉到那么深的谷底是根本没有希望活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花却自己走回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  身体已经变成一个空壳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:08:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都叹息说她成了「谷底回还者」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「谷底回还者」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个山谷里有时会出现这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉到谷底去  虽然活着回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心却像是被什么吃掉了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说如果谷中架起「一夜桥」的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也就是传闻罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一夜桥」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人见过在谷中只存在了一个晚上的桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经是很久以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像确实有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和现在附在花身上的是同一种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花被…附身了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一种被称作「伪葛」的藤蔓状虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没有看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是很难看得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这伪葛很脆弱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从反方向拉的话就很结实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和文献上看到的完全一样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳光已经照不到这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集到残留下的阳光中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里太缺乏阳光的照射了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  知道什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于你来说是个残酷的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「谷底回还者」和「一夜桥」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕都不是什么传闻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都可以用伪葛来解释
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然平常伪葛是寄生在树上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个山谷中的伪葛却会寄生在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄生在生物的体内而逃离谷底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们需要更多的日光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是自己却没有爬上山谷的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就会附在动物身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照射阳光  聚集力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的伪葛到达一定数量之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会从宿主身上出来  结成群落跨过山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迁移到更加适合生存的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概就是一夜桥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个山谷里  大约每二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会发生一次「虫的迁移」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  为什么那个时候「谷底回还者」会死？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些虫离开之后  不就应该恢复正常了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚我搜寻了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现这个谷底没有动物的尸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪葛寄生在尸体上的可能性很大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话  就算伪葛离开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只会变回尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  花也总有一天会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次听说有人看到了一夜桥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我爷爷出生的那一年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷今年六十岁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能让它延缓一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要求你把她救活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能让她再多活一阵子就可以了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样维持下去才是让她能活得最久的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把这虫驱除吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样做的话  十有八九她会当场身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为她这样活下去对她来说是幸福的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不做这种无谓的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果三年前那个时候她还活着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:13:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜桥出现之后  就会平安恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西会不会出现还不知道呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果花现在恢复的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一桩好婚事等着她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能让人家再等下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能接受你的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她已经不能被称之为「她」了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使如此也还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能当做物品来对待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  善
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这就要走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算明天去把桥修理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我家里去住一晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己一个人住在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然家人住在村里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是所谓被「处以私刑」流放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和村里人完全分离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有想过要一个人离开这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽然想过很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是花还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果花不在了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕很快就会离开了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于还是掉下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为你过了这桥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人也不会走这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  快点再重新建一座啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个时节大家都很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕会比较花时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那位虫师藏在这里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有话要和他说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它也是「谷地回还者」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许这里还有更多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里？你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是花吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是失去了记忆吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底对她做了什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过不要再接近花了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸停止了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花  振作点  花！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从脑袋里…爬出一条黑线一样的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善啊  你也赶快离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点离开比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也许今天晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会架起一夜桥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这边应该可以过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经聚集了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积攒力量到连你都能看得见的伪葛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了半夜时一定会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果放过这个机会  什么时候才能离开可就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗  没有任何留恋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座桥  想往回走就会掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定能够忘记她的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要离开这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？已经回不去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法走下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面有一条曾经是花…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！花在三年前就死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这三年间  是因为花还活着我才能撑过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看着她那副样子很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在更加确信了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩着她…我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别往回走！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后  他究竟怎么样了
